{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Welcome to your own pawn planet! This may not feel like a home yet but it will be, as soon as you clean it up and open your business. Here in your extraordinary shop, you'll meet customers from every corner of the galaxy. Learn the ins and outs of alien items, earthling memorabilia, and more, as you seek to purchase low and then sell high for the biggest profits. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But it's not just about the buying and selling. You'll also order parts to repair and restore the broken items that find their way into your shop, adding value and netting you even more <strong>Galactic Dollars</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your journey to become a <strong>legendary interstellar entrepreneur</strong> starts here. Welcome to the hustle of the galaxy, where every deal can either rocket you to fortune or plunge you into cosmic space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Make business with customers coming to your shop across the galaxy. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Order repair parts, fix broken items and earn more cash.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Attend storage auctions. Risk your money to only buy worthless storage or get lucky and find a fortune!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Upgrade your shop and Visit different planets and find rare items.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Make daring heists.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First 50K","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2479840/e5ad09d375f497c38dc0247f8ec3249ec79c746f.jpg"},{"name":"First 100k","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2479840/4ad1af9e38cbdaf688eeb12d7adaecaf30c96df9.jpg"},{"name":"First 500k","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/ap